value:
Summoning contract, huh? Then I'm
under your command, am I?! Gah-HA!
Maybe we are not so different!

Do not ask me of the Kingdom
of Múspell. I know nothing of it.
Mortals are of no consequence.

That weapon... Let me try it out.
Now, now! Don't be stingy!
Are we not on the same side?

It doesn't matter who they are—
everyone sounds the same when
they scream for mercy.

Mortals make little sense. You live
only a moment, and yet you worry
over the most meaningless trifles.

You are in the presence of the god
of flame!$k$p...Shouldn't you be making
an offering to me?
This is the shape of things.

An offering? I see you are beginning
to understand how to win my favor.

Master of flame, lord of one realm
of the nine... Múspell I am!

Sit down and listen.$k$pYou mortals... You lot have hot blood
running through your veins...$k$pBut now you use all these blades and
armored plates... Pah! What fakery.$k$pLong ago, when the mortals lived
uncovered, bare to the elements...$k$pBack then, there was a fire in the
bellies of mortals—a fire that could be
stoked into a raging flame at my will.$k$pThat same fire burns deep within
you as well... Let it out! Do as you
please! Take what's yours!$k$pIf anyone complains, stab them!
Let your true nature come forth!
Master of flame, lord of one realm of the nine... Múspell I am.
Beasts you are, and naked should you all be.
The end comes for you, Nifl. Soon.
Where's the fight in you?! Let's go already!
You dare let the word 'ally' fall from your fool mouth?
The nature of everything is to burn! Char the flesh, show me the bones! Lay bare the truth!
